22 (3) The assessments imposed by this section may be collected by the insurance carrier
23 from the insured. However, the insurance carrier shall not collect from the employer
24 any amount exceeding the assessments imposed pursuant to this section. If the
25 insurance carrier collects the assessment from an insured, the assessment shall be
26 collected at the same time and in the same proportion as the premium is collected.
27 The assessment for an insurance policy or other evidence of coverage providing a
